text: End of Days usually can mean: *End times in eschatology and religion. "End of Days" has also been the title of a number of movies and television episodes: *End of Days (1999 movie), starring Arnold Schwarzenegger and directed by Peter Hyams *"End of Days" (Buffy episode), a season 7 episode of Buffy the Vampire Slayer *"End of Days" (Torchwood), a series 1 episode of Torchwood
